{"tid":373582,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"將自己層樓按十二次，借夠一千萬再走佬其實有無可能架","createTime":"2017-08-25T06:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T00:19:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"508ffb7695d2a0dbe5cd081fa37582c03808555a","tid":373582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"假設層樓值三百萬，未供完,借埋貴利財仔"},{"pid":"750e799291c4c0a40b20f060d39d9c6211d930d5","tid":373582,"uid":125989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設層樓值三百萬，未供完,借埋貴利財仔</blockquote><br />\nwhy not"},{"pid":"e1a8d7de0f34e2876ae7a645eeb383c0fccdc495","tid":373582,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"業主懵然不知<br />\n<br />\n在眾多sub-mortgage中，以東亞銀行造得最多。記者在西貢一獨立別墅找到業主Gloria Law，她今年三月以一千五百多萬，買入這個背山面海的別墅一個單位自住，並於同月向財仔GIC借一千二百萬元樓按。根據金管局按揭指引，<span style=\"color: red;\">這類千萬豪宅，銀行最多只可借五成，不受監管的財仔，則借幾多都有！</span>羅小姐便借足八成。只有三十多歲，打扮入時的羅小姐說：「搵GIC都係貪方便，夠簡單。見佢賣咁多廣告唔會有咩古怪，但利息貴銀行六釐！」按土地註冊處資料顯示，GIC在今年六月，再將這物業連同豪宅紀雲峰及元朗工廈等，共七個由其他不同業主持有的已抵押物業，再抵押予東亞銀行，亦即sub-mortgage。記者向羅小姐透露此情況，她驚訝地表示毫不知情：「真係o架？」她更乘機向記者投訴GIC：「我唔知！而且我一直同佢哋講想借一千萬，點知到簽約時，先知佢哋預備咗一千二百萬，氹我借多啲﹗」"},{"pid":"9515f0cd43e6abcfd641783a09d81850604436b2","tid":373582,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a43f0f90baf5bb68417bb67a5cd134c16ce7e7f","tid":373582,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"金管唔會管的"},{"pid":"35bba7aa122316ecb018d918ee8ad7f801969987","tid":373582,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"阿努阿圖係咪一千萬可以移民？"},{"pid":"8ee69f50eead2f0bd75c9ab0b1702c959e192c64","tid":373582,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"可以架"},{"pid":"6ad7fb036a4ccad1d3359ebf992adfffd84d15d4","tid":373582,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"財仔自己有內部聯網<br />\n你唔到按到第二次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"d75660bb0cdf88884f7f0b763578a7f0e2b8f554","tid":373582,"uid":130513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c529338aab7fc338cc33c397a92ca7d44b3ed1b","tid":373582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43657a0079b9a67bdaa550d0a4f2c4232013dc53","tid":373582,"uid":42509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"借完移民，十年唔好返香港應該冇問題"},{"pid":"ea8607f64c01bf015f758bc4897cd181086f407b","tid":373582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78d8e7f9d70850f6d4ad73271bc0f2f67dd49ac","tid":373582,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"填土廳幾多按睇到架喎"},{"pid":"394494a6c62c9b06bd02816b4956490c01ef0de3","tid":373582,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/108899.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F9%2F108899.html&d=YkKN8ErseoKdUdwvRorTiE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=cdc33154\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/9/108899.html</a>"},{"pid":"b1114a143c6ad7696acbb1df0bf1d4987b7d9284","tid":373582,"uid":89343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T00:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借完移民，十年唔好返香港應該冇問題</blockquote><br />\n有咁大筆債移民，著草以後唔番黎先有得諗"}]}